of us even have sales assistants for friends and have often asked them for a favour or two during peak shopping season.
But what we can all admit to is that we have always wished it was easier than to go down to the store in dense traffic, 
navigating through throngs of fashionistas, all vying for the same trendy clothing items, waiting in line to try on our 
top picks in the trial rooms, etc.
        </p>
        <p id="p1">
Well, you can do all this from the comfort of your home while enjoying many online shopping benefits, right from 
